 from Mapdiva is easy to operate and still offers powerful drawing tools.","Artboard’s tagline, &#34;Simple. Powerful. Fun.&#34;, is accurate. The layout of this software is easy enough for beginners to understand, but it has enough depth that it doesn&#39;t feel limiting. Artboard offers a layout similar to Adobe Photoshop’s, with design tools on the left and right and the image in the middle. It gives you room to grow as you learn some of the advanced tools.","Even better for beginners is the Artboard user guide. This guide provides simple step-by-step instructions. Each piece of the guide includes detailed images of the software so you know exactly what tools and tricks are being explained. With its familiar layout and advanced user guide, Artboard is a good tool for those looking to jump into the Mac drawing app world."]},"id":"087419c6-22d4-4a83-a1a1-b9a2c935a795","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/QatXVHyubqkUBzYnuyfdNf.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"https://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/prod/large/52640-artboard-box.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/QatXVHyubqkUBzYnuyfdNf.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"QatXVHyubqkUBzYnuyfdNf","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/QatXVHyubqkUBzYnuyfdNf.jpg","alt":""},"id":"d5963d7c-abc9-4e4f-99fc-a1008f628d90","type":"image"},{"data":{"hawk":"{\"data-model-name\":\"Artboard\", \"data-widget-type\":\"price\"}","linkText":"Visit Site","url":"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/artboard/id1113889188?mt=12&uo=4&at=1l3v52U","specs":null,"subtitle":"","urlStyle":"button","review":{"rating":0,"url":"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/pictures-story/652-best-drawing-apps.html","name":"Artboard","id":""},"noFollow":false,"title":"<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/us/pictures-story/652-best-drawing-apps.html\">Artboard</a>","pros":["Empty List"],"cons":["Empty List"]},"id":"bc755c79-479f-462e-8f7b-4a968ad4f14e","type":"buying-guide"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Artboard by 